      <title>苹果生产中心受到关税的打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-03/apple-production-hubs-hit-by-tariffs-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果股（Apple Stock）周四受到打击，因为关税将击中公司的生产中心。彭博的马克·古尔曼（Mark Gurman）分解了这可能意味着技术巨头的供应链和定价。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-03/apple-production-hubs-hit-by-tariffs-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 20:22:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英特尔收益与TSMC的合资报告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/intel-shares-rally-after-report-of-joint-venture-with-tsmc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英特尔公司（Intel Corp.）的股票收益在一份报告中，该公司暂时同意台湾半导体制造公司的合资企业，这是陷入困境的美国芯片制造商的标志，这是一项备受期待的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/intel-shares-rally-after-report-of-joint-venture-with-tsmc</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 19:01:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储的厨师看到增长速度较慢，在关税的通货膨胀率中停滞不前</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/fed-s-cook-sees-slower-growth-stall-in-inflation-amid-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储州长丽莎·库克（Lisa Cook）说，她认为今年的经济增长速度较慢，并且在关税和其他政策变化的情况下降低通货膨胀方面的进展停滞，但决策者现在应该保持利率稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/fed-s-cook-sees-slower-growth-stall-in-inflation-amid-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 18:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国拥有国内供应商的股票，股息免于关税动荡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/tariff-turmoil-spares-stocks-with-domestic-suppliers-dividends</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者淘汰唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的关税范围（Broadside）的影响已经确定了一群潜在的赢家，这是一个重新连接的世界贸易秩序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/tariff-turmoil-spares-stocks-with-domestic-suppliers-dividends</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 17:03:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
