    <item>
      <title>S＆amp; p 500自covid自关税时遭受最坏的跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/s-p-500-tumbles-as-tariff-war-ignites-growth-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自大流行深度以来，美国股票跌落最多，随着总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的急剧新贸易关税激发了广泛的衰退恐惧，并让投资者寻求避风港债券以及日历。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/s-p-500-tumbles-as-tariff-war-ignites-growth-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 13:44:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自2020年以来，库存崩溃燃料最差的S＆amp; P 500天：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在全球市场中，“美国第一”贸易正在瓦解，股票与美元旁边急剧暴露在美国经济上。随着华尔街对唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税战争的叛乱加剧，商人正急于固定收入避风港。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 23:34:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
